{"tid":1296477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉拳毆強姦人妻同事 32歲男子：你係咪打畀警察","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T11:59:06.000Z","uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02e6db521b79954d8268065767b592512c98ba1d","tid":1296477,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"一名已婚女子五年前邂逅一起在餐廳工作的男同事，兩人發展婚外情。直至去年2月初，男同事涉嫌帶女事主回旺角通菜街劏房寓所後，先後拳毆及兩度強姦她，女事主趁男朋友外出用膳時逃出單位，並一度躲藏在大廈天台直至翌日凌晨才敢離開。男子一共被控強姦等三罪，今在高等法院受審。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vcoFzXKr.skVVhlJc9KFWA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190708a135247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvcoFzXKr.skVVhlJc9KFWA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190708a135247.jpg&h=4b6923e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n32被告陳國禎被控於2018年2月4日下午至翌日凌晨，在‪香港九龍旺角通菜街‬某大廈內非法囚禁和2度強姦36歲女事主。<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞指，被告去年2月4日中午致電事主，藉詞與她一起購物要求與事主相見，豈料見面後被告要求事主一起前往位於通菜街的劏房寓所單位。事主不情願下最終仍答應被告要求。稍後事主欲離開並返回工作崗位，但受到被告阻撓。事主上司懷疑她曠工並致電了解狀況，事主電話中哭訴求助，被告見狀便怒火中燒，一手奪去事主手機後毆打她的面部，其後更脫去事主衣服後強姦她。<br />\n<br />\n事主稍後趁被告出單位外徘徊，用被告手機發短訊給丈夫，惟事敗遭被告發現，被告揚言：「你係咪打畀警察。」然後再次毆打女事主。被告後來突然憐香惜玉，主動替事主塗藥膏，然後再次強姦她。<br />\n<br />\n被告完事後出外用膳，事主趁機逃出單位，但她怕下樓時遭被告碰過正著，反而向上跑並躲在大廈天台，直至翌日凌晨4點事主才敢逃出涉案大廈乘的士回家。期間事主借用「的哥」的手機向丈夫哭訴，丈夫聞訊後報警。"},{"pid":"44f65962be83b41da3f9e866edc6af60b6e5f280","tid":1296477,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"去人地間屋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2d503f239e41ffe5c62bc30b8cca74caa9b406","tid":1296477,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44f65962be83b41da3f9e866edc6af60b6e5f280","tid":1296477,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"去人地間屋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"同自願開部電話比警察一樣 冇得怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93ded0bcba1f14ee31772a57f159b0cc4a44ff9","tid":1296477,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:41:04.000Z","msg":"40都黎緊仲蠢過隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講以為十八廿二"},{"pid":"c414e62c6bcd79f31c6000a26f2a0ffea513309b","tid":1296477,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93ded0bcba1f14ee31772a57f159b0cc4a44ff9","tid":1296477,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:41:04.000Z","msg":"40都黎緊仲蠢過隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講以為十八廿二"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"陳雲仲老啦都選立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 青山冇分年齡"},{"pid":"b08b06a0b4e1638ca082c8d3d69de4201fd01e67","tid":1296477,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c414e62c6bcd79f31c6000a26f2a0ffea513309b","tid":1296477,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93ded0bcba1f14ee31772a57f159b0cc4a44ff9","tid":1296477,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:41:04.000Z","msg":"40都黎緊仲蠢過隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講以為十八廿二"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"陳雲仲老啦都選立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 青山冇分年齡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"痴線同蠢兩回事黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟人返屋企只有兩種情況：<br />\n妹妹仔入世未深/預左同個男人扑野"}]}